data.title: Map of the Lompoc Rancho [Calif.] : finally confirmed to Joaquin Carrillo et al. / surveyed under the orders of the U.S. Surveyor General by Ralph W. Norris, Deputy Surveyor, May 1859
data.meta_description: Includes table of boundaries and Surveyor General's certifications and seal.Pen-and-ink and watercolor on tracing cloth.From: U.S. District Court. California, Southern District. Land case 15 SD, page 60; land case map E-967 (Bancroft Library).Shows drainage, township lines, buildings, survey markers, boundaries, adjoining ranchos, etc.Relief shown by hachures.4362 L5238
